Package com.iha.emulator.models.value

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HasBooleanRandom
    Interface providing methods, that needs to be implemented by value, that want to use boolean generator.
    HasGenerator
    Interface providing methods, that needs to be implemented by values, that are using generator
    HasLinearDistribution
    Interface providing methods, that needs to be implemented by value, that want to use linear distribution generator.
    HasNormalDistribution
    Interface providing methods, that needs to be implemented by value, that want to use normal distribution generator.
    Status
    Interface used for values represented as status.
    Value<T>
    Interface providing method declarations needed to implemented by every value.
    VPTRegulatorValue
    Interface implemented by values emulating VPT regulator.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractValue<T>
    Abstract class providing implementation of Value interface methods used by all specific value implementations.
    ValueFactory
    Class used to create new instances of values.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Value.Generator
    Enum containing description of generators for new values.
    Value.Type
    Enum containing all types of implemented values with their default information.
